<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Public Fruit Tree Map</title>
<style>
body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
text-align: center;
background:#f6f6f6;
margin:0; 
}

h1{
margin-top:20px;
}

.map-container{
margin:auto;
width:90%;
max-width:900px;
}

iframe{
width:100%;
height:600px;
border:none;
}

.button {
display:inline-block;
margin:15px;
background:#2E7D32;
color:white;
padding:12px 20px;
border-radius:8px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>🌳 Public Fruit Tree Map</h1>

<p>Community map of publicly accessible fruit trees.</p>

<a class="button"
href="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=11sHwMPYBX-T3l5ueNSub7386vMiHfFI"
target="_blank">
Open in Google Maps
</a>

<div class="map-container">
<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=11sHwMPYBX-T3l5ueNSub7386vMiHfFI&ehbc=2E312F&noprof=1"></iframe>
</div>

</body>
</html>
